item.title: Lieb-Thirring type estimates for Dirichlet Laplacians on spiral-shaped domains
item.description: arXiv:2406.00580v1 Announce Type: new Abstract: In this paper we derive Lieb-Thirring estimates for eigenvalues of Dirichlet Laplacians below the threshold of the essential spectrum on asymptotically Archimedean spiral-shaped regions.
item.dc:creator: Juan Bory-Reyes (Schneiderova), Diana Barseghyan (Schneiderova), Baruch Schneider
